OL,3,C'Scene of devastation' Community
OL,4,Crallies together after car ploughs
OL,5,Cinto pub
OL,7,FA community in Kent has rallied
OL,8,Ftogether to rescue a pub after a car
OL,9,Fploughed into the building, leaving a
OL,10,F"scene of utter devastation".
OL,12,FThe car crashed into The Pilot Inn in
OL,13,FDungeness in the early hours of Sunday
OL,14,Fmorning (10 August).
OL,16,FRachel and Niko Miaoulis have owned
OL,17,Fthe pub for 25 years.
OL,19,FMr Miaoulis said: "It was devastating.
