OL,3,C'Scene of devastation' Community
OL,4,Crallies together after car ploughs
OL,5,Cinto pub
OL,7,F"We turned up 20 minutes after it
OL,8,Fhappened and it was just a scene of
OL,9,Futter devastation.
OL,11,F"The main structural supports of this
OL,12,Fpart of the building were on top of
OL,13,Fthe car.
OL,15,F"There was dust and debris everywhere,
OL,16,Fglass everywhere.
OL,18,F"The staff that had already turned up
OL,19,Fwere just shell shocked and some of
OL,20,Fthem were in tears as we were."
