OL,7,FWithin an hour of the crash, staff and
OL,8,Flocals arrived to help with clean-up
OL,9,Fefforts, working through the night.
OL,11,FThe efforts from the community meant
OL,12,Fthe pub was able to reopen for
OL,13,Fbusiness just hours after the crash.
OL,15,FMr Miaoulis said: "This is our busiest
OL,16,Ftime of year.
OL,18,F"We employ 46 full time staff, a lot
OL,19,Fof these staff have got
OL,20,Fresponsibilities and children and
OL,21,Fmortgages.
