OL,3,C'Scene of devastation' Community
OL,4,Crallies together after car ploughs
OL,5,Cinto pub
OL,7,F"So it's important for us for them to
OL,8,Fstill have their income.
OL,10,F"For us, the longer we're closed for,
OL,11,Fthe more likely customers are to go
OL,12,Fsomewhere else and possibly not come
OL,13,Fback.
OL,15,F"We didn't want that business
OL,16,Finterruption which is why 12 hours
OL,17,Fafter it happened we were open."
OL,19,FThe couple hope they will be able to
OL,20,Fuse the damaged part of the building
OL,21,Fwithin the next ten days.
