OL,7,FKent Police have since charged Howard
OL,8,FSargeant, of Coat Drive, Romney Marsh,
OL,9,Fwith drink driving and driving whilst
OL,10,Funfit.
OL,12,FThe 52-year-old was bailed and will
OL,13,Fappear before Folkestone Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt on 27 August.
